Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This video is a special video brought to everyone by Shogakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When watching this video, please keep the room bright and sit away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:46.36,Title,,0,0,0,,CONAN, KID, AND THE CRYSTAL MOTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This luxury train is our pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Royal Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you find it, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have actually made a very special reservation for her Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No. I wanted to meet the Japanese, even for a little, so I requested this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Selizabeth\NQueen of the Principality of Ingram
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:14.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, the Japanese government feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:15.81,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shinna Jikan\NMinistry of Foreign Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was even able to meet one famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you talking about Inspector Nakamori, who was responsible for escorting you?{Oh, are you talking about the man in charge of your escorting, Inspector Nakamori}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was the person I met in my private room a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the thief, Kaito Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You met with Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you really{Are you sure}, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stand back. This gentleman is from the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what exactly was Kid doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came to steal the treasure of our Ingram Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:02:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The largest topaz in Europe, Crystal Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the note that we received was real...{I suppose that notice that we received was a real one...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he not manage to take the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only took a glance for him to realize...{One glance was enough for him to understand...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It's fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real one is well hidden elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Your Majesty, where might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something I can't even tell the Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid may very well be eavesdropping on this discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Kid is on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search everyone suspicious!\NSearch all passengers from beginning to end{head to toe}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I cannot allow you to disturb the rest of the passengers for the sake of the Queen of Ingram.{Kaizou: our Ingram Empire}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still two and a half hours before we reach Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may try to steal the jewel as he wrote in the note...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I will protect it, and I'm willing to risk the name of my country for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mother...{Kaizou: Hey, ma'am.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SIlence. Actually, didn't I tell you that you're not supposed to leave the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how many times have I told you to call me "Your Majesty" in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:38.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip. Son of the late Ingram's ruler,\NHenry, and Her Majesty{Kaizou: Highness}, Selizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Phillip\NHeir to the Principality of Ingram
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the heir to the throne of Ingram Empire.{Kaizou: He's the crown prince of the Ingram Empire.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But that jewel looks different than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:56.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He probably planted it when\Nhe went into Her Majesty's room.{a few minutes ago}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can you hear me, Kaito Kid!?{Kaizou: Hey! Are you listening, Kaito Kid?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As long as I'm here, you won't lay a finger on this jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm here, you won't lay a finger on this jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:15.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was just yelled at by your father, damn inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you getting mad for? Weren't you the one who wanted to ride this train?{What's with the frown? You're the one who wanted to ride this train.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked my dad for tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I'm immensely{always} grateful to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you'd better get your act together.\NWe're going to meet Her Majesty later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty's probably in the saloon right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I made an appointment and I'm going to greet Her Majesty with:{So I just booked an appointment, so I can go up to her and say:}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm the daughter of Inspector Nakamori,\Nwho always gets beat by Kid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay! We really are lucky, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're riding on the same train as Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to thank Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nand the others{??} for inviting us to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:14.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is Inspector Nakamori escorting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be that Kaito Kid\Nsent a warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the saloon car?\NWe might able to meet Her Majesty.{Maybe I'll get a chance to meet Her Majesty.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, let's go. I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perhaps we'll meet Kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but the saloon car is fully booked for tonight.{I'm sorry, but all tables in the saloon car have been booked for today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having a lot of visitors today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but when we get to Osaka, we'll definitely get to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I can't sit here and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have to find out whether or not Kid sent a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:24.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, because of Kid and his unnecessary warnings, this place is crawling with cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it won't be as easy to get that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, wouldn't it be easier to steal it from Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gotten in our way too many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the confusion, I'll take Her Majesty's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect opportunity to become a famous sniper in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, isn't it about time to tell me where you're hiding the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't know its whereabouts, I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried, then please stay by my side and protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm on duty right now, so wine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are the first person to refuse my offer, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've changed my mind, one glass won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew Europe had the best wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you start, you can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, this is my daughter Aoko\Nand her classmate, Kaitou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two said that they had to be on the same train as Her Majesty, so I couldn't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kaitou said that he had to see Her Majesty at all costs, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoko, don't get in the way of the security!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And you call this security?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, at least I got into the saloon car with Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I can search for the jewel's hiding place to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What good fortune for Kid{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sama{\r\be10}.{Kaizou: for His Majesty, Kid.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But... where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I checked earlier, so I don't think\Nit's in Her Majesty's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means it must be within her reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A cat? No way...{The cat? It can't be...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Kaitou, you've been staring at Her Majesty for a while now.{Kaitou, are you aware that you've been staring at Her Majesty for a while now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! I was looking around\Nthe saloon and saw Her Majesty's cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Caesar? Cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's turning two this year.{He'll be two years old soon.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip Maximilian of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caesar, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, this is Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me hold him for a second!{Can I hold him for a second?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone under the table.{Kaizou: He went under the table.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a naughty cat.{Kaizou: He's troublesome, this little guy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:59.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right eye looks normal. Left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Kaitou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, it's just a normal cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute stuffed animal{doll}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad gave it to me, it's my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me see it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like it's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kaito Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop joking like that. Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I was wrong, though I know where the jewel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip, it's dangerous here.\NPlease hurry back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty is not pleased with your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:11:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going, I have to protect mother and the jewel from Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're worried about your mother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to be caring and kind,\Nbut she changed after Father passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always gets mad at me,\Nand never listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she{'s come to hate} hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I promised to my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would protect my mother and my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like no matter how many times\NI say it, you still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's not "mother", but "Her Majesty".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forbid you to leave this room again! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, leave it. He won't understand until I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're Prince Phillip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. As I thought, Kid sent a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a kid, but already a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can find the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know where my mother hid it.{Actually, I don't know where my mother hid it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to hide a leaf, hide it in the forest.{Where would a wise man hide a leaf? In the forest.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, now you can't tell which piece I just moved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there is no forest, you make your own{one yourself}.{If there were no forest, he would make a forest.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like in Gilbert Keith's story{novel}\N"The Sign of the Broken Sword", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these are the words of a famous detective\Nsaid to be Sherlock Holmes' rival, Father Brown.{Yeah, it's a line from the famous detective said\Nto be Sherlock Holmes' rival, Father Brown. / Yeah, these are the words of Father Brown,\Na detective said to be Sherlock Holmes' rival.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the story{novel}, the trick was more violent and frightening, but your mother's trick is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I think she did a much more devious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want to hide a leaf, hide it in the forest.{Where would a wise man hide a leaf? In the forest.}\NIf there is no forest, you make your own{one yourself}."{If there were no forest, he would make a forest.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's why my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was probably after Kid stole it...{After she met Kid, she probably... // very unsure about that line}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know so much about Kid, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's because we're closely related{Kaizou: forever connected}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How troublesome, I got the wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Papa, pay attention!{be careful}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man was clearly eavesdropping. Is he Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... I've seen that face somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to the restroom and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just running around like that.{You can't just run around in the carriages!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be in Osaka in ten minutes.{Kaizou: There's ten minutes until we get to Osaka.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like even the famous\NKaito Kid didn't accomplish his goal.{Looks like our genius Kaito Kid will be left with nothing today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, the victory is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems that way, doesn't it?{It looks like it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where is the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you as soon as we get to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how about another glass? To victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where in the world is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn. If I don't hurry up, I'll run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where did I see that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, I can't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange... it hasn't changed in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Usually{Normally} the shape would...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To victory!{Cheers!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see, now I know...{That's it... I understand now...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}where the jewel is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a save trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It even has pressed flowers on it, and it smells nice.{Even the flowers are squeezed out! And it smells good!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't become Kid in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was on the Professor's computer!{I saw him on the Professor's computer!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:31.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jackal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is Jackal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The world-famous jewel thief.{Kaizou: He's internationally known as a jewel thief.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a brutal one...{He's also famous for his cruelty...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a blackout!{The lights went out!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has Kid finally shown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand! I was only protecting Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one is your glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you, divide them up and check each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you have hid the jewel in my glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Mother is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is a great honor to be deceived by you again, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid? You fool, we're on a train.\NThere's nowhere for you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, please remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid is like a ghost in your bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And do not forget that before you're a Queen, you are a mother with a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Halt, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing? After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's emergency! Let us pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of me, the treasure of our country{Kaizou: the country's fortune} is now lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're as naive as ever, Inspector.{How easy it is to distract you, Inspector.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always falling for that dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the naive one, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, the people of my country will be in trouble, so give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan? I see. So he's on this train, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to get up here, that uncle helped me.{And this uncle helped me to climb up here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's behind me, the kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've waited for this moment, Kaito Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't have time{for games.} to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put the jewel down and turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want the kid to die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, don't give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice... Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always given me a hard time...\NCome on, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The immortal Kaito Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...will meet his end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:41.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If this guy's the Jackal, then the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your socks are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were white before,\Nwhen'd you change them?{They used to be white...\NWhen did you change them?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:09.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you're going to disguise yourself,\Nthen do it properly, Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought, he got out of here.{Kaizou: As I thought, it was that man.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means, Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? This is someone else's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} him. He wouldn't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give back the jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for? And is that what you say to the one who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, the people of my country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope! I'm not giving it back to a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're doing this for your mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to return the jewel\Nso your mom will praise you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's an even better way to reveal your mom's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip, Phillip...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me mother, I chased after Kaito Kid\Nto retrieve the stone, but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ever listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you always do dangerous things?{Why do you get into all kinds of trouble?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why then did I become stricter,\Ntrying to replace your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But... Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're okay... thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:19.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You see, Prince,{Kaizou: That's great, Prince.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:23.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your mom's a genuinely grief stricken Queen of Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, boys don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are to call me Your Majesty.{Call me "Your Majesty".}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and the others are waiting for us at the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.79,0:24:42.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That jewel is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:45.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that Kid didn't manage to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:46.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.87,0:24:51.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next time, I'll get to the Jewel of Destiny.
